title: Joe Rogan Experience Review of Dr. Cornel West and Rico Verhoeven
description:
Dr. Cornel West is an American philosopher and a super interesting speaker. Joe and him get into so much from the genius of musicians to the philosophers of the past.. Rico is the Glory world champion kick boxer and a seriously bad ass dude. He will straight up kick anyone head off..

Enjoy my review folks!
